T02TD1527E:84b-1: shr'i badzra d'a ki n'i k'a ya ni dharmma n'a ma /
T02TD1527E:84b-3: dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro lus med pa'i chos zhes bya ba ;
T02TD1527E:84b-4: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1527E:84b-5: gang zhig 'jigs rung dur khrod chen por phat phat rngam pa'i sgra sgrogs shing /
T02TD1527E:84b-6: mkha' 'gro za byed mun pa'i nang na zla shar lta bur rab tu 'bar //
T02TD1527E:84b-7: h'um h'um zhes brjod sha za ro langs ma mo'i tshogs rnams skrag mdzad pa //
T02TD1527E:84b-8: gsang sngags gsang mdzod mnga' bdag bde chen rgyal mo'i sku la 'dud //
T02TD1527E:84b-10: padma rin chen chu bo'i gzhung //
T02TD1527E:84b-11: seng ge glang chen ri dags ltar //
T02TD1527E:84b-12: nyi ma me dang shel dang mtshungs //
T02TD1527E:84b-14: skal ldan rnams kyis rtogs par gyis //
T02TD1527E:84b-15: rang bzhin chos dbyings rnam dag dbyer med bde ba chen po'i klong //
T02TD1527E:84b-16: dag ba'i gzhal yas chos kyi 'byung gnas rdo rje'i btsun mo ste /
T02TD1527E:84b-17: sha za smyon pa bu chung bzhin //
T02TD1527E:84b-18: sprin dang nam mkha' glog bzhin du //
T02TD1527E:84b-19: ce sbyang ro langs sa ra sa //
T02TD1527E:84b-21: skal ldan rnams kyis nyams su long //
T02TD1527E:84b-22: rgyal ba rnams kyi rtag tu mnyam gzhag 'od gsal chen po'i ngang //
T02TD1527E:84b-23: dus gsum dag tu rgyun mi 'chad pas sangs rgyas sku gsum de rang bzhin //
T02TD1527E:84b-24: bdag gzhan dbyer med ngo bo nyid dpal lhun grub dbyer med spros dang bral //
T02TD1527E:84b-28: gcer bu gling pa rgyal po blangs //
T02TD1527E:84b-29: blon po sna bsgyur rta mchog ste //
T02TD1527E:85a-0: @85a * // bran dang lam chen btsun mo'o //
T02TD1527E:85a-1: skal ldan rnams kyis rtogs par gyis //
T02TD1527E:85a-3: dam pa bde chen mgon po skye med rang byung sangs rgyas yin //
T02TD1527E:85a-5: smin grol sems kyi rgya mdud shig / phyi nang gsang ba mthar thug pas //
T02TD1527E:85a-6: dbang gis rnam par rtog pa'i rgya //
T02TD1527E:85a-7: mdud pa sems nyid rang grol du //
T02TD1527E:85a-8: rtog pa'i dra ba bshig pa yin //
T02TD1527E:85a-9: rang bzhin med pa'i dang la gzhag par bya //
T02TD1527E:85a-10: dam tshig rang sems me long ltas //
T02TD1527E:85a-11: aa ham srog rtsa ba sam ta //
T02TD1527E:85a-12: sems nyid rang gsal me long la //
T02TD1527E:85a-13: dbang gi 'bras bur mthar phyin pas //
T02TD1527E:85a-14: log rtog 'khor ba'i dri ma phyis //
T02TD1527E:85a-15: gdod nas dag pa kun gzhi'i rgyud //
T02TD1527E:85a-16: mi med rig la dag pa la //
T02TD1527E:85a-17: snang med rig tsam rgyun du ltos //
T02TD1527E:85a-18: dam rdzas rtogs pa'i nyi ma ni //
T02TD1527E:85a-19: bde chen rang sems spros dang bral //
T02TD1527E:85a-20: rtsa rlung byang sems mi 'gyur ba'i //
T02TD1527E:85a-21: gnyis med rdo rje gang gis rtogs /
T02TD1527E:85a-22: de ni rdzas kyi dam ba mchog / phyi ltar snang ba sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1527E:85a-23: rtog pa'i nyi ma gcig la 'de //
T02TD1527E:85a-24: de la gsal 'grib med pa yin //
T02TD1527E:85a-25: spyod pa chu la ral gri rgyob //
T02TD1527E:85a-26: gang dang gang snang de dag la //
T02TD1527E:85a-27: spyod du med pa'i ngang nyid las //
T02TD1527E:85a-28: spyad par gyis shig rnal 'byor ba //
T02TD1527E:85a-29: chu la ral gris gang btab pa //
T02TD1527E:85a-30: rjes med dag tu 'gro ba bzhin //
T02TD1527E:85a-31: nyam da med pa'i ral gri yis //
T02TD1527E:85a-32: spas dang brtul zhugs bhu su ku //
T02TD1527E:85a-33: mnyam rjes med par spyod pa bya //
T02TD1527E:85a-34: rig pa sems kyi spyod pa gyis //
T02TD1527E:85a-35: rang grol phyag rgya chen po ltos //
T02TD1527E:85a-36: rang sems gnyis med phyag rgya che //
T02TD1527E:85a-37: rang grol sems kyi dang du grol //
T02TD1527E:85a-38: phyag ni stong pa'i ye shes yin //
T02TD1527E:85a-39: rgya ni 'khor ba'i rgya dang bral //
T02TD1527E:85a-40: chen po zung du 'jug pa yin //
T02TD1527E:85a-41: ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid de //
T02TD1527E:85a-42: bde chen dri med dang du ltos //
T02TD1527E:85a-44: dpal ldan rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1527E:85a-45: nam mkha' stong pa'i dang las ni //
T02TD1527E:85a-46: brda skad brag ca ji bzhin du //
T02TD1527E:85a-47: stong pa'i dang las snying rje'i sgra //
T02TD1527E:85a-48: dbyer med bde chen dang du rdzogs //
T02TD1527E:85a-49: skal ldan blo yi padma de //
T02TD1527E:85a-50: ye shes nyi ma shar ba yis //
T02TD1527E:85a-52: blo ldan dri med gzi brjid khyod //
T02TD1527E:85a-53: bu la ha ri'i dgon pa ru //
T02TD1527E:85b-0: bho ta'i ma rig mun @85b sel la //
T02TD1527E:85b-1: ye shes snang pas khyab par gyis //
T02TD1527E:85b-2: rje to lo chen pos na ro pa la gsungs pa'o /
T02TD1527E:85b-4: // / dpal 'khor lo sdom pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1527E:85b-5: rtsa rlung dra ba'i 'khor lo bskor //
T02TD1527E:85b-6: rtsa ni lus la gnas pa ste //
T02TD1527E:85b-7: aa ba dh'u t'i la la n'a //
T02TD1527E:85b-8: ra sa n'a ste dbye ba yang //
T02TD1527E:85b-10: dra ba zhes bya ba 'brel te //
T02TD1527E:85b-11: rlung ni las kun byed pa can //
T02TD1527E:85b-12: lnga yi bdag nyid bcu ming ste //
T02TD1527E:85b-13: rlung sems gnyis su med par ni //
T02TD1527E:85b-14: mi rtog 'khor lo bskor bar bya //
T02TD1527E:85b-15: rig pa ye shes sgron me som //
T02TD1527E:85b-16: rig pa sems kyi rgyal po ste //
T02TD1527E:85b-17: lhun grub dang du ye shes kyi //
T02TD1527E:85b-18: sgron me gnyis su med par 'bar //
T02TD1527E:85b-19: ma rig pa yi mun bsal nas //
T02TD1527E:85b-20: ye shes dri bral snang bas khyab //
T02TD1527E:85b-21: ro snyoms phyi yi me long ltos //
T02TD1527E:85b-22: 'byung ba bzhi po ro snyoms dang //
T02TD1527E:85b-23: shes pa ting 'dzin ro snyoms te //
T02TD1527E:85b-24: nyams ni bde gsal rnam pa bzhi //
T02TD1527E:85b-25: skye ba med pa'i me long la //
T02TD1527E:85b-26: dran pa'i rdul gyis bkab pa de //
T02TD1527E:85b-27: dran med rig pa'i nyams kyis phyi //
T02TD1527E:85b-28: sems kyi me long dag pa la //
T02TD1527E:85b-29: snang ba gnyis mad lta ba la //
T02TD1527E:85b-30: rnam rtog shugs byung dri ma phyis //
T02TD1527E:85b-31: bde chen gsung gi rin chen chongs //
T02TD1527E:85b-32: bde ba rang rig gsal ba ste //
T02TD1527E:85b-33: chen po bla ma dam pa'i gsung //
T02TD1527E:85b-34: zag bcas lus kyi bde ba las //
T02TD1527E:85b-35: zag med ro mnyam dbyer med pa //
T02TD1527E:85b-36: gsang ba mchog gi dbyer med pa //
T02TD1527E:85b-37: bdud rtsi zhal rnyed snying po 'di //
T02TD1527E:85b-38: rin chen lta bur rang gzhan don //
T02TD1527E:85b-39: 'byung bas skal ldan dam pas chongs //
T02TD1527E:85b-40: rnal 'byor dbang phyug te lo chen po yis //
T02TD1527E:85b-41: rgyan gyi ri zhes grags par bdag la gnang //
T02TD1527E:85b-42: gsang sngags snying po lus med rdo rje'i tshig / zab mo'i man ngag n'a ros bdag la gnang //
T02TD1527E:85b-43: lnga brgya'i tha mar gyur te sa steng du //
T02TD1527E:85b-44: snod ldan rnams kyi blo yi padmo de //
T02TD1527E:85b-45: kha ba can ljongs khyed kyi slob ma yis //
T02TD1527E:85b-46: 'dul par gyur zhes bla ma'i gsung las thob //
T02TD1527E:85b-47: 'gro rnams bde mchog 'bras bu rgyas gyur cig //
T02TD1527E:85b-48: dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro lus med pa'i chos zhes bya ba rdzogs so//
